schools.name: Rodger & Ellen Beck J High School

data.description: A recently remodeled house with new porcelain floor tiles , located in a 24-hour manned gated community. High ceilings in the family room opens to the kitchen and breakfast room. Lots of natural light comes in through the owner’s suite is on the first floor with an ample closet. The owner’s suite bathroom includes a shower and jacuzzi tub, double sinks, and a private WC. Upstairs, a big bright game room with 2 identical bedrooms with walk in closets, 2nd full bathroom, and a 4th bedroom with en-suite full bathroom. Big bonus - the laundry room is upstairs! Large yard with a nice stamped concrete patio with a pergola. House is located steps away from the community grounds with trails, pool, multiple playgrounds, tennis courts, basketball courts, clubhouse, and an onsite gym. Refrigerator, washer & dryer are part of the offering.
